76
00:09:23,340 --> 00:09:25,300
Réponds-moi.

77
00:09:26,980 --> 00:09:28,100
Mlle Lin...

78
00:09:28,660 --> 00:09:30,580
Elle s'est sacrifiée.

79
00:09:31,700 --> 00:09:33,300
Sacrifié?

80
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,269
Rapide.

81
00:09:35,270 --> 00:09:36,390
Ici.

82
00:09:36,860 --> 00:09:37,489
Dépêchez-vous.

83
00:09:37,490 --> 00:09:38,579
Ici.

84
00:09:38,580 --> 00:09:39,539
Nous n'avons pas le temps, mademoiselle.

85
00:09:39,540 --> 00:09:40,860
Vous devez y aller maintenant.

86
00:09:41,550 --> 00:09:42,820
Mademoiselle, dépêchez-vous.

87
00:09:45,540 --> 00:09:47,100
Assurez-vous que cela parvienne à Shen Gu.

88
00:09:47,460 --> 00:09:48,580
Mademoiselle.

89
00:09:49,180 --> 00:09:50,179
- Aller.
- Mademoiselle.

90
00:09:50,180 --> 00:09:53,420
- Aller.
- Manquer!

91
00:09:53,500 --> 00:09:57,180
Manquer!

92
00:09:57,900 --> 00:09:59,419
Courir!

93
00:09:59,420 --> 00:10:00,740
Mademoiselle.

94
00:10:02,460 --> 00:10:05,140
Manquer!

95
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:17,760
